---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Creative Writing" activePage="creative" description="Creative writing benchmark results for local LLMs on AMD Strix Halo">
  <div class="page-header fade-up">
    <h1>Creative Writing</h1>
    <p class="description">Two benchmark suites test creative writing quality: a short story generator scored on narrative quality, and a single-chapter style adherence test scored against a human reference. These go beyond speed &mdash; they evaluate actual output quality.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Short Story (2,000 words)</h2>
  <div class="card fade-up">
    <p>Generates a ~2,000-word short story with specific narrative requirements: character setup, inciting event, conflict, emotional vulnerability, and a closing hook. Scored /30 across 6 quality categories including voice, pacing, sensory detail, dialogue, and emotional depth.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="table-wrap fade-up">
    <table class="sortable">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Model</th>
          <th>Backend</th>
          <th data-type="number">Words</th>
          <th data-type="number">Time</th>
          <th data-type="number">Speed (w/s)</th>
          <th data-type="number">Quality</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3-30B-Instruct-2507 UD-Q4_K_XL <span class="badge champion">Champion</span></td><td>RADV</td><td>1944</td><td>68s</td><td>29</td><td class="best">30/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-122B-A10B UD-Q4_K_XL (thinking)</td><td>RADV</td><td>2285</td><td>313s</td><td>7.3</td><td class="best">29/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B UD-Q4_K_XL (thinking)</td><td>RADV</td><td>2257</td><td>103s</td><td>22</td><td class="best">28/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-122B-A10B Unsloth-UD-Q4 (defaults)</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>2002</td><td>269s</td><td>7.4</td><td>28/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3-Coder-Next-80B</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>2384</td><td>87s</td><td>27</td><td>26/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Ling-Flash-2.0</td><td>RADV</td><td>2197</td><td>124s</td><td>18</td><td>26/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Ministral-3-14B-Instruct</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>2318</td><td>205s</td><td>11</td><td>26/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B UD-Q4_K_XL (no-think)</td><td>RADV</td><td>2098</td><td>95s</td><td>22</td><td>26/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B UD-Q4_K_XL (b8546, defaults)</td><td>RADV</td><td>1945</td><td>109s</td><td>17.8</td><td>25/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Nemotron-3-Super-120B-A12B (no-think)</td><td>ROCm</td><td>3132</td><td>308s</td><td>10.2</td><td>25/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-27B UD-Q4_K_XL (Unsloth params)</td><td>RADV</td><td>1886</td><td>377s</td><td>5.0</td><td>25/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Devstral-2-123B</td><td>RADV</td><td>2164</td><td>1108s</td><td>2</td><td>25/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Nemotron-3-Nano-30B</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>2000</td><td>60s</td><td>33</td><td>24/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">MiniMax-M2.5 IQ3_XXS</td><td>RADV</td><td>2045</td><td>161s</td><td>13</td><td>24/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Kimi-Linear-48B Q5_K_M</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>1833</td><td>54s</td><td>34</td><td>23/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Magistral-Small-2509</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>861</td><td>138s</td><td>6</td><td>21/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Solar-Open-100B</td><td>RADV</td><td>4506</td><td>246s</td><td>18</td><td>21/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">GPT-OSS-120B</td><td>ROCm</td><td>2467</td><td>101s</td><td>24</td><td>20/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Mistral-Large-2411</td><td>AMDVLK</td><td>1223</td><td>669s</td><td>1.8</td><td>20/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-9B UD-Q4_K_XL (Unsloth params)</td><td>RADV</td><td>2263</td><td>260s</td><td>8.7</td><td>20/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Devstral-Small-2-24B</td><td>ROCm</td><td>2431</td><td>269s</td><td>9</td><td>16/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-4B Q8_0</td><td>RADV</td><td>1784</td><td>71s</td><td>25</td><td>16/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Nemotron-Cascade-2-30B-A3B Q8_0 (no-think)</td><td>RADV</td><td>3153</td><td>82s</td><td>39</td><td>18/30</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">GPT-OSS-20B-Derestricted MXFP4</td><td>RADV</td><td>2014</td><td>65s</td><td>31</td><td>13/30</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h3>Short Story Findings</h3>
  <ul class="findings fade-up">
    <li><strong>Qwen3-30B is the undisputed champion</strong> &mdash; perfect 30/30 at 46 w/s, no reasoning leak, all narrative beats hit with literary quality.</li>
    <li><strong>Thinking mode adds ~2 quality points</strong> &mdash; 122B goes from 28 to 29/30, 35B from 26 to 28/30. Requires Unsloth-recommended sampling params and 64k context.</li>
    <li><strong>Qwen3.5-35B-A3B with thinking matches 122B defaults</strong> (~28/30) at 3x the generation speed (22 vs 7 w/s). The most practical high-quality option.</li>
    <li><strong>Sampling params matter enormously</strong> &mdash; Unsloth-recommended params (presence_penalty 1.5, top_k 20, enable_thinking via chat-template-kwargs) transformed results across all Qwen3.5 models.</li>
    <li><strong>GPT-OSS-120B and Solar-Open-100B</strong> expose reasoning/planning text before the story (instruction-following issue).</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <h2>Single Chapter (Style Adherence)</h2>
  <div class="card fade-up">
    <p>Generates a full chapter (~2,500 words) following a detailed style guide and outline. Tests adherence to specific constraints: POV and tense, punctuation rules (no colons/semicolons, limited em dashes), sensory hierarchy, and 7 required narrative beats. Scored against a human-written reference chapter (2,495 words, 0 violations).</p>
  </div>

  <div class="table-wrap fade-up">
    <table class="sortable">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Model</th>
          <th data-type="number">Words</th>
          <th>Beats</th>
          <th>Colons</th>
          <th>Em Dashes</th>
          <th>Notes</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Human (reference)</td><td>2495</td><td>7/7</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>Publishable quality</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B UD-Q4_K_XL (b8546, defaults)</td><td>1065</td><td>7/7</td><td class="best">0</td><td class="best">1</td><td>Perfect style, very short, 68/80</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B UD-Q4_K_XL (no-think)</td><td>3474</td><td>7/7</td><td class="best">5</td><td class="best">1</td><td>presence_penalty 1.5 eliminated loop</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-122B-A10B Unsloth-UD-Q4 (defaults)</td><td>3880</td><td>7/7</td><td class="best">5</td><td class="best">1</td><td>Best 122B prose result</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-27B UD-Q4_K_XL (Unsloth params)</td><td>3456</td><td>7/7</td><td>12</td><td>3</td><td>presence_penalty 1.5 cut overshoot</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-9B Q8_0</td><td>3549</td><td>7/7</td><td>5</td><td>4</td><td>Strong opening, world-building miss</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-4B Q8_0</td><td>3326</td><td>7/7</td><td>3</td><td>4</td><td>Close to 9B quality</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">MiniMax-M2.5 IQ3_XXS</td><td>3124</td><td>7/7</td><td>7</td><td>4</td><td>Best prose quality</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3-Coder-Next-80B</td><td>2497</td><td>7/7</td><td>4</td><td>23</td><td>Strongest character voice</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">GPT-OSS-120B</td><td>2180</td><td>7/7</td><td>~5</td><td>~5</td><td>Workmanlike prose</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Kimi-Linear-48B</td><td>2157</td><td>7/7</td><td>3</td><td>19</td><td>Best style adherence</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3-30B Q8</td><td>1819</td><td>7/7</td><td>~8</td><td>~10</td><td>Fragmented, repetition loop</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Ling-Flash-2.0</td><td>1758</td><td>7/7</td><td>~6</td><td>~8</td><td>Dense, purple prose</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">GPT-OSS-20B-Derestricted</td><td>1643</td><td>7/7</td><td>24</td><td>~5</td><td>Short, heavy colon abuse</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Nemotron-3-Super-120B-A12B UD-Q4_K_XL</td><td>1590</td><td>7/7</td><td>14</td><td>4</td><td>Undershoot target, heavy colons</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Nemotron-Cascade-2-30B-A3B Q8_0 (no-think)</td><td>2428</td><td>7/7</td><td>3</td><td>17</td><td>Heavy em dashes, 3 tense slips</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-122B-A10B UD-Q4_K_XL (Unsloth no-think)</td><td>4298</td><td>7/7</td><td>15</td><td>1</td><td>Unsloth params worse for 122B prose</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B UD-Q4_K_XL (thinking)</td><td>5121</td><td>7/7</td><td>11</td><td>1</td><td>Overshoot with thinking; no-think better</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="model-name">Qwen3.5-35B-A3B (default params)</td><td>19000+</td><td>7/7</td><td>varies</td><td>varies</td><td>Loop caused by missing presence_penalty</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h3>Chapter Findings</h3>
  <ul class="findings fade-up">
    <li><strong>No model matched human prose quality</strong> &mdash; the reference text remains the benchmark to beat.</li>
    <li><strong>Qwen3.5-35B-A3B prose loop FIXED</strong> &mdash; was not an architecture issue. Unsloth-recommended <code>presence_penalty=1.5</code> eliminates the loop entirely (3,474 words, 5 colons in no-think mode).</li>
    <li><strong>No-think mode best for prose style</strong> &mdash; thinking mode overshoots (5,121 words for 35B, more colons). For romance quality, thinking wins; for prose adherence, no-think wins.</li>
    <li><strong>122B prose: defaults better than Unsloth params</strong> &mdash; 5 colons with defaults vs 15 with Unsloth no-think params. Presence_penalty 1.5 hurts 122B prose.</li>
    <li><strong>Kimi-Linear-48B best style adherence</strong> &mdash; only 3 colons, 0 semicolons across the entire chapter.</li>
    <li><strong>MiniMax-M2.5 best overall prose quality</strong> &mdash; visceral action writing, strong character voice, touch-dominant sensory detail.</li>
  </ul>

  <script is:inline>
    document.querySelectorAll('table.sortable th').forEach((th, i) => {
      const arrow = document.createElement('span');
      arrow.className = 'sort-arrow';
      arrow.textContent = ' \u25B4';
      th.appendChild(arrow);
      let asc = true;
      th.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const table = th.closest('table');
        const tbody = table?.querySelector('tbody');
        if (!table || !tbody) return;
        const rows = Array.from(tbody.querySelectorAll('tr'));
        const isNum = th.dataset.type === 'number';
        table.querySelectorAll('.sort-arrow').forEach(a => { a.classList.remove('active'); a.textContent = ' \u25B4'; });
        arrow.classList.add('active');
        arrow.textContent = asc ? ' \u25B4' : ' \u25BE';
        rows.sort((a, b) => {
          const av = a.children[i]?.textContent?.trim() ?? '';
          const bv = b.children[i]?.textContent?.trim() ?? '';
          if (isNum) return asc ? parseFloat(av) - parseFloat(bv) : parseFloat(bv) - parseFloat(av);
          return asc ? av.localeCompare(bv) : bv.localeCompare(av);
        });
        rows.forEach(r => tbody.appendChild(r));
        asc = !asc;
      });
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
